QuestData.Title: Envenomed Spider Fang
QuestData.Description:
Even wary bees have been known to fall prey to these enormous spiders. They lie in wait near flowerbeds and ambush them while they collect their harvest. Thanks to you, they have one less spider to worry about.
The Hivemother will be interested in this item.
QuestData.LogDescription: Take the Envenomed Spider Fang to the Honeyback Hivemother for a reward.
QuestData.QuestCompletionLog: Take the Envenomed Spider Fang to the Honeyback Hivemother for a reward.
